results.name: A(n, k) = [x^k] DedekindEta(x)^n, square array read by descending antidiagonals, A(n, k) for n >= 0 and k >= 0.
comment: The columns are generated by polynomials whose coefficients constitute the triangle of signed D'Arcais numbers A078521 when multiplied with n!.
